# Figma and UI

- Use **design tokens** (CSS variables / Tailwind theme) — avoid one-off hex in many places.
- **Match layout and spacing** from specs; ask if design is ambiguous.
- **Responsive** breakpoints as in design system.
- **Accessibility**: semantic HTML, labels, focus states, contrast.
- Prefer **existing UI primitives** in the repo over new ad-hoc styles.
